; Regression test for issue #835: Having trouble with -Y from the command line (BZ#835)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/835
; Tests that -Y (--yearly) flag correctly groups register output by year when
; specified on the command line.

2010/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

2010/06/20 Gas
    Expenses:Auto    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

2011/03/10 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $200.00
    Assets:Checking

2011/09/05 Gas
    Expenses:Auto    $75.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg -Y Expenses
10-Jan-01 - 10-Dec-31           Expenses:Auto                $50.00       $50.00
                                Expenses:Food               $100.00      $150.00
11-Jan-01 - 11-Dec-31           Expenses:Auto                $75.00      $225.00
                                Expenses:Food               $200.00      $425.00
end test
